# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# REQUIRED at BUILD time (Vite inlines import.meta.env.* into the bundle).
# These MUST be set in the Cloudflare Pages / CI build environment, otherwise the
# production bundle ships placeholder values ("missing-key" / "Bearer undefined")
# and every Supabase request 401s. The build now fails loudly if these are unset.
#
# The Supabase URL + publishable (anon) key are PUBLIC by design — they are safe
# to expose in the client. Access control comes from Row-Level Security, not from
# keeping these secret. NEVER put the service_role key in a VITE_ var.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_SUPABASE_URL="https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co"
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="YOUR_SUPABASE_ANON_PUBLISHABLE_KEY"

# Privy auth — the app id is a public client identifier (not a secret).
VITE_PRIVY_APP_ID="YOUR_PRIVY_APP_ID"

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIONAL — only needed if/when the on-chain payment flow is actually wired up.
# (As of now there is no live contract write in src/; these are unused.)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_CONTRACT_ADDRESS="0x3ACA071D6cA66462612d04eB6f31Ab7924F86FF0"
VITE_RPC_URL="https://mainnet.base.org"
VITE_WALLET_CONNECT_PROJECT_ID="YOUR_WALLET_CONNECT_PROJECT_ID_HERE"

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SERVER-SIDE ONLY — set these as Supabase Edge Function secrets, NOT here and
# NOT with a VITE_ prefix (a VITE_ prefix would bundle them into the public client).
#   PRIVY_APP_SECRET            — Privy server secret (for token verification)
#   SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY   — provided by Supabase to functions automatically
#   LOVABLE_API_KEY             — paid LLM gateway key
#   OX_API_KEY                  — 0x swap API key
#   WEBHOOK_API_KEY             — shared secret for cron/webhook-only functions
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
